{
  "title": "Fluffy Peppery Mexican Chicken Tacos",
  "description": "A crowd-pleasing Sonoran dish featuring tender chicken, reduced grape juice, and anti-inflammatory friendly spices, all wrapped in a fluffy taco.",
  "cuisine": "Mexican",
